text: Reality vs. The Optimist is the debut album by Kiss Kiss, released on February 6, 2007 on Eyeball Records. They created a music video for the song "Machines." The band also recorded a live music video for the song "The Cats In Your House". ==Track listing== #"Janet" – 4:15 #"Iris and Eye" – 3:25 #"Sixth Sense" – 2:45 #"A Conch to the Ear" – 0:30 #"Machines" – 2:35 #"Satellite" – 3:36 #"Shits In Suits (Dress Up)" – 2:16 #"The Friend Who Bends His Bolts At Fiends" – 0:11 #"The Cats In Your House" – 2:35 #"The Most Beautiful Birth Ever Endured" – 0:27 #"Vagabond" – 5:29 #"Stay the Day" – 4:18 ==References== Category:Kiss Kiss (band) albums Category:2007 debut albums
title: Reality vs. the Optimist
